//**********************************************************************
//*   CREATE REPORT OF UPDATES TO PANVALET
//**********************************************************************
//STEP0040 EXEC PGM=&PGM305
//*STEPLIB  DD DSN=SYS2.DUMMY.LOADLIB,DISP=SHR
